title._content: Marion County 4-H club members on KOAC radio broadcast, 1950

description._content: Original Collection: Extension and Experiment Station Communications Item Number: P120:2883 Item Description: Marion County 4-H club members and leader are making a radio appearance. From left: Freddie Parker, 12; Mrs. Gay Fabry, leader; Charmaine Roguski, 13; Jerry Simmons, 13; and Kay Knickerbocker, 12, all of Salem, Oregon.
